// PART 3 — STUDENT DASHBOARD
// =====================================================
// Contains:
//   [1] Student dashboard HTML (sidebar + pages)
//   [2] Student home page (welcome + stats + notices)
//   [3] Folder browser (class-wise, lock-aware)
